# Nexus Field three-layer boundary — IDE anti-drift contract

**Canonical decision:** [ADR-0035](../../docs/decisions/0035-three-layer-surface-ide-anti-drift.md) · [ADR-0038](../../docs/decisions/0038-nexus-field-governed-composition.md) · Layer 1 seal: [`app/(main)/[locale]/o/[orgSlug]/nexus/_SEAL.md`](../../app/(main)/[locale]/o/[orgSlug]/nexus/_SEAL.md)

**If this rule and `AGENTS.md` diverge, follow `AGENTS.md` and fix this rule in the same PR.**

Mechanical guard: [`tests/unit/nexus-surface-contract.test.ts`](../../tests/unit/nexus-surface-contract.test.ts)

---

## Prime directive

```txt
Layer 1 — app/           → URL + thin re-exports ONLY
Layer 2 — lib/features/  → getNexusSnapshot, list-surface builders, nexus-field-page
Layer 3 — components2/   → NexusFieldView, orientation band, truth map, Lynx summon
```

**Single snapshot rule:** one `getNexusSnapshot` per request; builders are pure over snapshot slices.

---

## Layer 1 — `app/.../nexus/`

```tsx
export {
  generateNexusFieldMetadata as generateMetadata,
  NexusFieldPage as default,
} from "#features/nexus/server"
```

**Forbidden:** `#components2/nexus`, `getNexusSnapshot`, builder calls in routes.

---

## Layer 2 — `lib/features/nexus/`

| Concern | Path |
| --- | --- |
| Snapshot query | `data/nexus-snapshot.queries.server.ts` |
| List builders | `data/nexus-*-list-surface.server.ts` |
| Page orchestrator | `components/nexus-field-page.server.ts` |
| Path helpers | `constants.ts` → `organizationNexusPath` |

**Governed sections:** pressure, priority lanes, resolutions (`governed:list-surface`).

**Handcrafted (Layer 3):** orientation band, truth map.

**Forbidden at module root:** `_SEAL.md`

---

## Layer 3 — `components2/nexus/`

**May import:** `#features/nexus` (types/constants), `#components2/metadata`, `#components2/ui/*`.

**Forbidden:** `getNexusSnapshot`, list builders, `#features/nexus/server` from client files.

---

## Verification

```bash
pnpm lint:path -- lib/features/nexus components2/nexus
pnpm test:fast -- tests/unit/nexus-surface-contract.test.ts
pnpm typecheck
```
